<p>ChatGPT is the most versatile AI writing tool for students. Use it to brainstorm essay topics, create outlines, improve sentence structure, and even get feedback on your drafts. Its free tier is generous enough for regular coursework.</p>
<p class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
